In Angola, from May, October, 2022, we had an increase of over 265,000 Bible studies.

00:22:25.380 --> 00:22:33.380
In the lands under the Central America branch, we're now reporting over 680,000 Bible studies.

00:22:33.380 --> 00:22:39.380
That's over 20% more studies than we reported in May of 2022.

